Class TreeNode<KType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • TreeNode<KType>
  • Type Parameters:
    KType - the type of node values
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LeafNode

    public class TreeNode<KType>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a node class that encapsulates one node in the QuestionTree. TreeNodes are used to hold object properties.
